      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison at 3 L/min, 2500 RPM",
      "description": "Comparison of CFD-predicted velocity magnitude fields against particle image velocimetry (PIV) measurements in the pump volute. Mean absolute error across 1200 interrogation windows is 0.08 m/s (4.2% of peak velocity). Turbulence intensity predictions show moderate agreement. Uncertainty in experimental PIV measurements (laser sheet thickness, particle seeding density) is discussed qualitatively in the validation report section 4.3 but no formal UQ artifact is linked here.",
      "comparisonMetric": "Mean absolute error: 0.08 m/s (4.2% of peak velocity)",
      "agreementAssessment": "Adequate for flow topology; marginal for near-wall shear stress"
    },
    {
